title: $3900-3/2 South Ft Lauderdale FURNISHED House-Parking for Boat/RV
neighborhood: Southwest Ft Lauderdale - South of Davie Blvd-West of I-95
posting_body: ['Comfortable and wonderful family home with 3 BRs, 2 BTHs, 2 family rooms, office space (perfect to work from home).', 'Relax and have fun in the beautiful garden with Seminole Tiki Hut, Zen water fountain, BBQ.', 'Rest in the hammock, bring your yoga mat, breath and relax.', 'Parking for RV or boats allowed.', 'Fully furnished, 1 King, 1 Queen, 2 Twins, big dining table, office space, 2 comfortable sofas, to make your life extra enjoyable.', 'Great location to enjoy the beach (19 Mins), Hard Rock Casino (10 mins), Sawgrass Mall (18 Mins), Whole Foods (10 mins), and FLL Airport (10 mins).', 'Easy to get on main hwys: 595, Turnpike & 95.', '4 BR home, 1 BR left for storage, 3 BR available.', 'Rent includes landscaping & internet.', 'THIS IS A YEARLY LEASE – NOT SHORT TERM.', 'Landlord requires First Month, Last Month and Security Deposit to move in (3 month’s rent).', ' Acceptable credit score/report for all persons on the lease (650+), background check and PROOF of income showing sustained combined incomes at least 3 times the amount of the monthly rent.', 'Must have no judgments or money owed to previous landlords.', 'Dianne Warren,', 'show contact info', ', Beachfront Realty.', ' Map view is approximate, not exact, for security reasons.', 'Please CALL to view this property.', ' No texts or emails for first contact.', ' Private owner property.']
